VRChat utilizes multiple '''Discord servers''' to organize and manage different groups of VRChat users.

== Public servers ==
VRChat utilizes three public Discord servers for anyone within good standing to access. The user count has been updated as of February 10, 2026.

=== VRChat ===
[[File:VRChat Discord Icon.webp|thumb|VRChat|128x128px]]
Created on July 20, 2017. This server is the primary server for VRChat and its community, with approximately ~375,000 users. It can be accessed at https://discord.gg/vrchat.

