== Private servers ==

There are few official VRChat Discord servers that are private, and available by invite only. The invites to these servers are handed out to people enrolled in obscure VRChat programs, typically for closed testing or moderation.
=== VRChat General Testing ===

''See also [[Special:MyLanguage/Quality Assurance|Quality Assurance]] for more detailed information.''

Also referred to as "Green", VRChat General Testing is a private server dedicated to communication for various types of closed beta tests. [[File:VRChat green Discord Icon.webp|thumb|VRChat General Testing|128x128px|none]]

=== VRChat Community Testers ===

''See also [[Special:MyLanguage/Quality Assurance|Quality Assurance]] for more detailed information.''

The '''VRChat Community Testers''' server consists of a select few community members chosen by the VRChat QA team, for their exceptional dedication to providing a numerous quantity of high-quality bug reports. They assist and communicate directly with the QA team on internal testing and bug fixes.[[File:Community_Testers_Server.png|thumb|VRChat Community Testers|128x128px|none]]

=== VRC World & Group Sellers ===
This server serves as where [[Worlds|world]] creators and group owners selected for the [[Creator Economy]] program are able to communicate with VRChat regarding the Creator Economy, and vice-versa.
[[File:VRChat CE Discord Icon.webp|thumb|VRC World & Group Sellers|128x128px|none]]
=== VRC Avatar Marketplace Sellers ===
This server serves as where [[Avatars|avatar]] creators selected for the [[Avatar Marketplace]] program are able to communicate with VRChat regarding the Avatar Marketplace, and vice-versa.
[[File:VRChat AVM Discord Icon.webp|thumb|VRC Avatar Marketplace Sellers|128x128px|none]]
=== VRChat Community Leaders ===
This server operates as a centralized place for community leaders to work together, share information between peers, report bugs and maintain a connection with the VRChat's community lead to help focus user feedback.

This server is joinable vai application process only, To join this server you must apply here in this [https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSdy0wu72WKl8iH43XEHMmzsrg3uGeRlQy2h59QUMZhrBN9djA/viewform Google Docs form]

The server was created on September 4, 2024. [[File:VRChat Community Leaders Discord Icon.webp|thumb|VRChat Community Leaders|128x128px|none]]
